Name: MX5 Crash Course
Info:
This is an example Championship - feel free to edit it or delete it! The EntryList for this Championship is open, so anyone can join and take part! 

MX5s are typically one of the most loved cars in Assetto Corsa, so expect a lot of people to join if you run these events!

Each event has a short qualifying, then a race and a second reverse grid (top 8) race. The second race points are affected by a 0.5x multiplier, so it is worth less than the first race.
